JACKIE.M_SU.116.A.DE: Da sind sie! Hol sie dir! Hol sie dir! Hol sie dir!
JACKIE.M_SU.116.A.EN: That's them! Get them! Get them! Get them!
JACKIE.M_SU.116.A.RU: Это они! Догони их! Догони их!

JACKIE.M_SU.161.A.DE: Beeil dich, Mann. Sonst entkommen sie.
JACKIE.M_SU.161.A.EN: Hurry up man! They're getting away!
JACKIE.M_SU.161.A.FR: Plus vite ! Ils vont se barrer !
JACKIE.M_SU.161.A.IT: Fai in fretta, amico! Stanno scappando!

JACKIE.M_SU.162.A.DE: Warte hier. Ich hol die Uhren.
JACKIE.M_SU.162.A.EN: Hang on. I'll get the watches.
JACKIE.M_SU.162.A.FR: Bouge pas, je vais chercher les montres.

JACKIE.M_SU.526.A.EN: Ram him. Take out his car.
JACKIE.M_SU.526.A.IT: Vagli addosso. Distruggi la sua auto.
JACKIE.M_SU.526.A.PO: Walnij w niego. Rozwal mu samochód.

JACKIE.M_SU.530.A.EN: Don't let him get away, man.
JACKIE.M_SU.530.A.FR: Le laisse pas se tirer, vieux.
JACKIE.M_SU.530.A.SP: No dejes que se escape, tío.

JACKIE.M_SU.531.A.DE: Da fährt unsere ganze Beute davon.
JACKIE.M_SU.531.A.EN: That's our whole score driving away.
JACKIE.M_SU.531.A.FR: C'est notre butin qui se fait la malle !
JACKIE.M_SU.531.A.IT: Tutto il nostro bottino se la fila.
JACKIE.M_SU.531.A.RU: Если он смоется, мы останемся безо всего.
JACKIE.M_SU.531.A.SP: Se nos esfuma todo el botín.

JACKIE.M_SU.534.A.DE: Noch mal. Ramm ihn. Ramm ihn, Mann!
JACKIE.M_SU.534.A.EN: Again. Hit him. Hit him, man!
JACKIE.M_SU.534.A.PO: Jeszcze raz. Walnij go! Walnij go!
JACKIE.M_SU.534.A.RU: Опять. Мочи его! Давай, стукни его!

JACKIE.M_SU.901.A.DE: Wir haben's geschafft, Mann! Wir haben's geschafft!
JACKIE.M_SU.901.A.EN: We did it, man! We did it!
JACKIE.M_SU.901.A.FR: On l'a fait, mec ! On a réussi !
JACKIE.M_SU.901.A.IT: Ce l'abbiamo fatta, amico! Ci siamo riusciti!
JACKIE.M_SU.901.A.PO: Udało się, stary! Udało się nam!

WEI.M_SU.041.A.DE: Hast du nicht gesagt, das wird ein Spaziergang?
WEI.M_SU.041.A.EN: I thought you said this was gonna be easy!
WEI.M_SU.041.A.FR: Tu m'avais pas dit que ce serait facile ?
WEI.M_SU.041.A.IT: Credevo avessi detto che sarebbe stato facile!
WEI.M_SU.041.A.RU: Кто-то помнится, говорил, что дело будет легкое?
WEI.M_SU.041.A.SP: ¡Dijiste que esto iba a ser fácil!
